      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Begin by securing API credentials and configuring your environment. The inference endpoint typically follows a RESTful structure, such as "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "POST /v1/tts/synthesize",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". Use JSON payloads to specify text input, voice parameters (e.g., voice_id, pitch), and output format. Implement authentication via API keys in request headers, and handle responses with status codes like 200 for success or 4xx/5xx for errors. For example:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "code_block",
        "lang": "json",
